headline: Is Mosaic (MOS) Pricing Reflect Long Term Value After Recent Share Price Rebound
summary: Wondering if Mosaic's share price around US$28.04 still offers value, or if the easy gains are already behind it? This article walks through what the numbers are actually saying about the stock. Over shorter periods the picture is mixed, with a 0.4% decline over the last 7 days, a 16.1% gain over 30 days, a 12.1% gain year to date, a 1.2% gain over 1 year, a 39.9% decline over 3 years and a 13.4% gain over 5 years.
